#: guix/scripts/build.scm:435
msgid ""
"Usage: guix build [OPTION]... PACKAGE-OR-DERIVATION...\n"
"Build the given PACKAGE-OR-DERIVATION and return their output paths.\n"
msgstr ""
"Χρήση: guix build [ΕΠΙΛΟΓΗ]... ΠΑΚΕΤΟ-Η-ΠΑΡΑΓΩΓΗ...\n"
"Δόμηση του δοθέντος ΠΑΚΕΤΟΥ-Η-ΠΑΡΑΓΩΓΗΣ και επιστροφή των διαδρομών εξόδου τους.\n"

#: guix/scripts/build.scm:437 guix/scripts/archive.scm:89
msgid ""
"\n"
"  -e, --expression=EXPR  build the package or derivation EXPR evaluates to"
msgstr ""
