msgid ""
"Usage: guix substitute OPTION [ARGUMENT]...\n"
"Internal tool to substitute a pre-built binary to a local build.\n"
msgstr ""
"Χρήση: guix substitute ΕΠΙΛΟΓΗ [ΟΡΙΣΜΑ]...\n"
